          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-gisela-stuart" title="Ms Gisela Stuart">Ms Stuart</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            My hon. Friend might be encouraged to know that the Maltese have suggested that we should also include the discovery of the deep sea.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0401P0-04804'>
        <a name='S6CV0401P0_20030320_WH_67'>  </a>
