            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_330wh' title='Col. 330WH &mdash; HC Deb 20 March 2003 vol 401 c330WH' name='column_330wh' href='#column_330wh' rel='bookmark'>330WH</a>
            have been shot to pieces? Does he not agree that it has to do with fundamental interests and not just with rhetorical bandyings on the side?
          </p>
